Subject: How to Work with People on the Spectrum: A Brief Discussion About Autism
Description: Did you ever wonder or even know that 95% of autistic people (ASD) are unemployed or underemployed? This panel will inform you of the misinformation surrounding autism and how we can help autistic people after high school or even college. Be yourself and not somebody else.  Speakers include:Ian Sterrett, Greg Walters, Tammy Morris - Track: Life  - Duration: 1 hour
